where she and my father were living.

560
00:51:48,010 --> 00:51:50,221
In the jungle?

561
00:51:50,346 --> 00:51:52,807
My father was a great adventurer.

562
00:51:59,271 --> 00:52:04,318
One day the great king
of the silver baboons

563
00:52:04,443 --> 00:52:09,198
