597
00:55:33,235 --> 00:55:35,738
My health was still poor.

598
00:55:35,863 --> 00:55:38,908
Cos of the risk of infection.

599
00:55:42,244 --> 00:55:46,874
People were so used to staying away
from me that they always stayed away.

600
00:55:49,752 --> 00:55:51,796
I never got close to people.

601
00:55:54,632 --> 00:55:58,135
Jeez. That's gotta be hard on a kid.

602
00:55:59,261 --> 00:56:03,641
Not being held
or being allowed to hold anyone.

603
00:56:10,022 --> 00:56:12,066
What does your father do?

604
00:56:15,069 --> 00:56:16,987
Uh...

