00:56:55,526 --> 00:57:00,197
Well, first guy to walk out of my life,
certainly not the last.

615
00:57:01,991 --> 00:57:03,284
Weird, huh?

616
00:57:03,409 --> 00:57:07,913
You're always stayin' away from love,
I'm always chasin' love.

617
00:57:08,038 --> 00:57:10,082
Weird.

618
00:57:43,657 --> 00:57:45,701
Come on.

619
00:59:05,531 --> 00:59:07,575
Here.

