with a room full of
strangers and relatives?

648
01:02:39,161 --> 01:02:41,205
Adam.

649
01:02:43,916 --> 01:02:45,960
Oh, oh.

650
01:02:47,628 --> 01:02:49,880
Star light, star bright,
first star I see tonight,

651
01:02:50,005 --> 01:02:53,634
I wish I may, I wish I might,
have this wish I wish tonight.

