I mean, what's up with this?

684
01:05:33,961 --> 01:05:38,674
Yeah, he speaks.
No, I haven't met his family.

685
01:05:39,967 --> 01:05:42,928
- He's an orphan.
- Really?

686
01:05:43,053 --> 01:05:45,973
No shit. I never met a real orphan before.

687
01:05:46,098 --> 01:05:48,184
Yeah.

688
01:05:48,309 --> 01:05:50,644
He's a lot smarter than people think.

689
01:05:50,770 --> 01:05:52,813
He reads a lot. Got a lot of books.

690
01:05:54,607 --> 01:05:56,817
He's really into his music.

691
01:05:56,942 --> 01:05:58,277
Really?

692
01:05:58,402 --> 01:06:03,199
