two guys tried to rape me.

705
01:07:02,425 --> 01:07:04,677
Oh, my God.

706
01:07:04,802 --> 01:07:07,263
Oh, my God. Caroline, are you OK?

707
01:07:08,431 --> 01:07:13,185
Yeah. Someone stopped them.
It was Adam. He saved me.

708
01:07:14,937 --> 01:07:17,898
Why didn't you tell me this?
Why didn't you come to me?

709
01:07:18,023 --> 01:07:20,067
I didn't tell anybody.

710
01:07:21,110 --> 01:07:23,154
Jesus, you poor thing.

711
01:07:24,113 --> 01:07:26,949
Are you all right?
