712
01:07:27,074 --> 01:07:29,326
Yeah?

713
01:07:29,452 --> 01:07:31,495
God, I don't believe this.

714
01:07:34,832 --> 01:07:36,250
Holy shit.

715
01:07:36,375 --> 01:07:38,419
- Shit, shit, shit.
- What?

716
01:07:39,545 --> 01:07:42,006
What?

717
01:07:42,131 --> 01:07:44,383
You're gonna be so mad at me.

718
01:07:45,760 --> 01:07:47,303
Why?

719
01:07:47,428 --> 01:07:51,098
Well, I kind of told Nick that
you would double with Ronnie.

720
01:07:51,223 --> 01:07:54,226
I... Great. Thanks a lot.

721
01:07:56,228 --> 01:07:58,397
Look, you don't have to go, OK?

722
01:07:58,522 --> 01:08:02,276
I mean, you could just forget
the whole thing, OK? Just forget it, OK?

723
01:08:02,401 --> 01:08:03,944
Well...

724
01:08:04,069 --> 01:08:06,238
Well, go anyway, OK? Just go, Caroline.

725
01:08:06,363 --> 01:08:09,158
I mean, you'll have a good time.
He's really nice.

726
01:08:09,283 --> 01:08:12,411
His father owns a hardware store
downtown, you know?

727
01:08:12,536 --> 01:08:14,997
When was the last time
we went dancing, huh?

728
01:08:15,122 --> 01:08:20,002
And, look, if you don't like him, he doesn't
turn out to be the glass-slipper man,

729
01:08:20,127 --> 01:08:22,963
you don't have to see him
any more, all right?

730
01:08:24,715 --> 01:08:26,759
